<i>charting an entirely</i>
<i>different course.</i>

01:00.693 --> 01:02.195
- Bulleit rocks.

01:02.262 --> 01:04.597
<i>narrator: Marcus Watkins</i>
<i>had always adapted</i>

01:04.697 --> 01:07.233
<i>as a means of survival,</i>
<i>carefully constructing</i>

01:07.300 --> 01:09.135
<i>chameleonic variations</i>
<i>of himself</i>

01:09.235 --> 01:11.638
<i>in order to present</i>
<i>a certain facade to the world.</i>

01:11.738 --> 01:14.874
<i>As a result, his own impulses</i>
